# Frontend (Feature-Sliced Design)

Структура: [docs/architecture/specs/frontend/12-frontend-app-architecture.md](docs/architecture/specs/frontend/12-frontend-app-architecture.md).

- Зависимости слоёв: `app → pages → widgets → features → entities → shared`
- HTTP-вызовы: `entities/*/api` через `shared/api/http`
- Страницы собирают widgets/features, не содержат прямых fetch
- Именование: [docs/ts-naming-conventions.md](docs/ts-naming-conventions.md), [docs/react-naming-conventions.md](docs/react-naming-conventions.md)
- TSDoc: [docs/coding-standards.md](docs/coding-standards.md) для `shared/api`, `entities/*/api`, экспортируемых компонентов
